com.snamp

Class Box<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snamp.Box<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Box<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a mutable (and not thread-safe) box for storing some object of the specified type. This class cannot be inherited.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Roman Sakno
    See Also:
